<L>__{interior hotel lobby. day}
<A>__{where five minutes before the lobby was a frenzy of wealthy europeans and aid workers, the groups of clustered black faces are silent except for the crying of babies and sobbing mothers. paul picks his way among them. zozo catches up.}
